---
title: Bacon & Beef Ravioloni with Chilli Tomato Sauce & Parmesan Rocket Salad
description: With pre-chopped, pre-marinated ingredients, our Fresh & Fast recipes are on the table in just 15 minutes. Perfect for busy weeknights - and busy people. Let’s add savoury beef mince and golden nuggets of bacon to veggie-filled pasta parcels in a tomato-based sauce - this quick dinner delivers bags of flavour!
